{"tid":113181,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"生存嘅意義唔通只有繁殖？","createTime":"2017-02-08T17:11:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T03:58:22.000Z","uid":35911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"39cb91750e8e0b037850dbdf9ed8062e3fbce5e6","tid":113181,"uid":35911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T17:11:17.000Z","msg":"其實人的生存既生物上意義為左繁殖而存在，並無特別意義，點解要生存，冇人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能啲父母扑嘢扑中咗你。<br />\n到底有咩可以令生存有番動力，行屍用走返工返學，然後死去？<br />\n失去左生存動力，生存其實再有冇意義？如果你唔繁殖，已經失去做人嘅意義，既然如此點解人類要高智商過其他生物，淨係有生存繁殖咪得囉，定係人唔單止需要生物繁殖既意義，仲要有心理上嘅生存意義，冇咗呢個心理嘅生存意義就好似老鼠失去多巴胺樣，見到嘢食都無胃口。<br />\n<br />\n點樣先可以尋找到呢個令到自己有生存嘅快樂？咁樣係唔係先算係真正生存意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb4ca09ee5e9218104e1ecc51d72d5392262def8","tid":113181,"uid":35911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T17:12:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"008d4dc8a1f7b36444b5ba455be4f2b2c8d12ca2","tid":113181,"uid":35911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T17:13:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f2bb763b3c4816978dce107d2d728f98e394f7","tid":113181,"uid":69133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T17:14:08.000Z","msg":"同自己講只係時間問題 一定有呢一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8093e30eaa6db26e4d08ef7ea43f64a4db5dcdd7","tid":113181,"uid":70264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T17:14:19.000Z","msg":"點論證繁殖係生存嘅意義 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"377bd9b7fdc9c4f13170f5d624f98e8c4871f255","tid":113181,"uid":70264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T17:15:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點論證繁殖係生存嘅意義 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n只怕連繁殖都唔係生存嘅意義 人無生存嘅意義 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"619d797c66eef5fee31ee6320be0b74951b387ef","tid":113181,"uid":35911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T17:16:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點論證繁殖係生存嘅意義 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所有生物都係為咗繁殖而生存 好似啲蟬 交完配就死啦 佢響地下生存咁耐 都係為咗呢一刻 繁殖"},{"pid":"0f4f1badb3ba995259688fe055413c6f1ae3d53c","tid":113181,"uid":35911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T17:16:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點論證繁殖係生存嘅意義 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n只怕連繁殖都唔係生存嘅意義 人無生存嘅意義 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0183242dd25f54560d5286cb82246df9305b783","tid":113181,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T17:20:04.000Z","msg":"其實係咁架啦<br />\n個個都冇權揀自己出唔出世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n讀書為左咩?<br />\n返工為左咩?<br />\n做人為左咩?"},{"pid":"57bfeab7d6fd3103132f436ee39b33e865e94368","tid":113181,"uid":80580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T17:22:21.000Z","msg":"呢個應該係義務唔係意義"},{"pid":"9dc4290cfc85582436dfbfbf354929ad060481af","tid":113181,"uid":35911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T17:27:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個應該係義務唔係意義</blockquote><br />\n義務係責任 意義作用和價值"},{"pid":"7a3ff9d2a83cf1c229254816fdec6c8d5fb90568","tid":113181,"uid":18384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T17:28:20.000Z","msg":"人高智商應該係無得解，自然進步出黎<br />\n生物既目的可能只有生存及繁殖，其他煩惱只係extra，鬼叫你人類生得聰明咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3520f3168affb5f1009fabed87331161c225be2c","tid":113181,"uid":35